intent.user_query: What is the total revenue generated from each product category (ProductType) in the year 2023, ordered from highest to lowest revenue?

phases.goal:
Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue
FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd
JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON sd.SaleID = s.SaleID
JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID
WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.SaleDate) = 2023
GROUP BY p.ProductType
ORDER BY TotalRevenue DESC;

arguments.sql:
SELECT p.ProductType, SUM(sd.Quantity * sd.UnitPrice) AS TotalRevenue
FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd
JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON sd.SaleID = s.SaleID
JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID
WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM s.SaleDate) = 2023
GROUP BY p.ProductType
ORDER BY TotalRevenue DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
